		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			As a lvl 14 cleric, I have found this weapon to have about worn out its usefulness.  But, from lvl9 to 14, I have used it extensively.  It has paid for itself many times over by allowing me to kill wisps for the Greater Lightstones.  And, I'll always have it.  Its been an invaluable spell for me.  It has allowed me to concentrate on picking up a little better armor instead of rushing out and spending 100pp on a magic weapon right away.  If you are a cleric..get it as soon as you can.  When you hit lvl 12, start solo hunting wisps with it.    
			</font>
	
		</td>
	</tr>
	
