			I rather like the Hammer of Wrath, I was able to <BR>
hunt magic creatures much earlier then all my <BR>
freinds.  Another nice thing is it can't be <BR>
disarmed succesfully, dueled a level 12 monk <BR>
using it and he kept dropping it back into my <BR>
inventory.  I used it until level 14 and was very<BR>
happy with it.  As for the Paladins complaint that<BR>
is very valid, but if you keep both your onehand<BR>
slash and one hand blunt maxed the HoW is the <BR>
cheapest magic weapon that a cleric or paladin <BR>
can get. 
